# Reference only — the master's backend list lives in haproxy.cfg (HAProxy doesn't
# read env vars). Documented here so the cluster's node map is in one obvious place.
#
# Node IPs (edit the `server` lines in haproxy.cfg to match):
#   JETSON_NODE=192.168.1.188
#   MACBOOK_NODE=192.168.1.99
#   WINDOWS_NODE=192.168.1.222
#
# Shared model served by every node:
#   LLM_MODEL=llama3.2:3b
